divs: sighting detailssighting report: on 10\26\2004 @ 9:11 pm, i was in out in my backyard in rural sw kansas looking at the southern sky, on a clear night. i had my camera with me = because i wanted to see how well the pictures would come out, for the = following night of the full moon eclipse. the sky was very clear, and = the stars were bright, as i was looking at the heavens , when i saw = something moving in the sky very strange. it was moving very fast up and = down, and horizontal. i could see that it had lights on it that were = different than a normal aircraft, and was in space. i could see the that = it was up close to the stars, but too far to get a really good sighting. = so, i took a picture of it with my hpix935 digital camera. later that = evening, i down loaded the photo from my camera to my laptop. i looked = at the photo in the windows photo program, and zoomed in on it. from the = photo you can see that it is some type of craft, and it s colors, as = well as the stars in the background. i believe that it was something = that was very interesting, so i showed the image to several other local = people, and asked their opinion. we all agreed that it should be = forwarded to an expert for analyst. please let me know what your opinion = is? if you would like to contact me by phone, you can reach me at = 480\832-0891. thank you, for your = cooperation.=20 taken 10\26\04 lakin,kansas =20 sincerely, jeff kunz po box 253 lakin, ks 67860=20 i
